       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COMP3-TEST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-BAL    PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3 VALUE 12345.67.
       01 WS-INT    PIC S9(5)V99 COMP-3 VALUE 3.50.
       01 WS-RESULT PIC S9(9)V99 COMP-3.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT = WS-BAL * WS-INT / 100
               ON SIZE ERROR
                   DISPLAY 'OVERFLOW'.
           DISPLAY WS-RESULT.
           STOP RUN.
